{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"For the next few minutes we're going to talk about energy,"},{"time":3000,"text":"and it's going to be a bit of a varied talk."},{"time":6000,"text":"I'll try to spin a story about energy,"},{"time":8000,"text":"and oil's a convenient starting place."},{"time":10000,"text":"The talk will be broadly about energy,"},{"time":12000,"text":"but oil's a good place to start."},{"time":14000,"text":"And one of the reasons is this is remarkable stuff."},{"time":17000,"text":"You take about eight or so carbon atoms,"},{"time":19000,"text":"about 20 hydrogen atoms,"},{"time":21000,"text":"you put them together in exactly the right way"},{"time":23000,"text":"and you get this marvelous liquid:"},{"time":25000,"text":"very energy-dense and very easy to refine"},{"time":27000,"text":"into a number of very useful products and fuels."},{"time":30000,"text":"It's great stuff."},{"time":32000,"text":"Now, as far as it goes,"},{"time":34000,"text":"there's a lot of oil out there in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"Here's my little pocket map"},{"time":38000,"text":"of where it's all located."},{"time":40000,"text":"A bigger one for you to look at."},{"time":42000,"text":"But this is it, this is the oil in the world."},{"time":44000,"text":"Geologists have a pretty good idea of where the oil is."},{"time":46000,"text":"This is about 100 trillion gallons"},{"time":49000,"text":"of crude oil"},{"time":51000,"text":"still to be developed and produced in the world today."},{"time":54000,"text":"Now, that's just one story about oil,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and we could end it there and say,"},{"time":58000,"text":"\"Well, oil's going to last forever"},{"time":60000,"text":"because, well, there's just a lot of it.\""},{"time":62000,"text":"But there's actually more to the story than that."},{"time":64000,"text":"Oh, by the way, if you think you're very far from some of this oil,"},{"time":67000,"text":"1000 meters below where you're all sitting"},{"time":70000,"text":"is one of the largest producing oil fields in the world."},{"time":73000,"text":"Come talk to me about it, I'll fill in some of the details if you want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76000,"text":"So, that's one of the stories of oil; there's just a lot of it."},{"time":79000,"text":"But what about oil? Where is it in the energy system?"},{"time":84000,"text":"Here's a little snapshot of 150 years of oil,"},{"time":87000,"text":"and it's been a dominant part of our energy system"},{"time":89000,"text":"for most of those 150 years."},{"time":92000,"text":"Now, here's another little secret I'm going to tell you about:"},{"time":96000,"text":"For the last 25 years,"},{"time":98000,"text":"oil has been playing less and less of a role"},{"time":101000,"text":"in global energy systems."},{"time":103000,"text":"There was one kind of peak oil in 1985,"},{"time":106000,"text":"when oil represented 50 percent of global energy supply."},{"time":108000,"text":"Now, it's about 35 percent."},{"time":110000,"text":"It's been declining"},{"time":112000,"text":"and I believe it will continue to decline."},{"time":114000,"text":"Gasoline consumption in the U.S. probably peaked in 2007"},{"time":116000,"text":"and is declining."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"So oil is playing a less significant role"},{"time":121000,"text":"every year."},{"time":123000,"text":"And so, 25 years ago,"},{"time":125000,"text":"there was a peak oil;"},{"time":127000,"text":"just like, in the 1920s,"},{"time":129000,"text":"there was a peak coal;"},{"time":131000,"text":"and a hundred years before that,"},{"time":133000,"text":"there was a peak wood."},{"time":135000,"text":"This is a very important picture of the evolution of energy systems."},{"time":138000,"text":"And what's been taking up the slack in the last few decades?"},{"time":141000,"text":"Well, a lot of natural gas"},{"time":143000,"text":"and a little bit of nuclear, for starters."},{"time":146000,"text":"And what goes on in the future?"},{"time":148000,"text":"Well, I think out ahead of us a few decades"},{"time":150000,"text":"is peak gas,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and beyond that,"},{"time":155000,"text":"peak renewables."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"Now, I'll tell you another little, very important"},{"time":159000,"text":"story about this picture."},{"time":161000,"text":"Now, I'm not pretending that energy use in total"},{"time":163000,"text":"isn't increasing, it is --"},{"time":165000,"text":"that's another part of the story. Come talk to me about it,"},{"time":167000,"text":"we'll fill in some of the details --"},{"time":169000,"text":"but there's a very important message here:"},{"time":171000,"text":"This is 200 years of history,"},{"time":173000,"text":"and for 200 years we've been systematically decarbonizing"},{"time":176000,"text":"our energy system."},{"time":178000,"text":"Energy systems of the world"},{"time":180000,"text":"becoming progressively -- year on year,"},{"time":182000,"text":"decade on decade, century on century --"},{"time":184000,"text":"becoming less carbon intense."},{"time":187000,"text":"And that continues into the future"},{"time":189000,"text":"with the renewables that we're developing today,"},{"time":191000,"text":"reaching maybe 30 percent of primary energy"},{"time":193000,"text":"by mid century."},{"time":195000,"text":"Now that might be the end of the story --"},{"time":197000,"text":"Okay, we just replace it all with conventional renewables --"},{"time":199000,"text":"but I think, actually, there's more to the story than that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"And to tell the next part of the story --"},{"time":203000,"text":"and this is looking out say 2100 and beyond."},{"time":206000,"text":"What is the future"},{"time":208000,"text":"of truly sustainable, carbon-free energy?"},{"time":210000,"text":"Well, we have to take a little excursion,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and we'll start in central Texas."},{"time":214000,"text":"Here's a piece of limestone."},{"time":216000,"text":"I picked it up outside of Marble Falls, Texas."},{"time":218000,"text":"It's about 400 million years old."},{"time":220000,"text":"And it's just limestone, nothing really special about it."},{"time":223000,"text":"Now, here's a piece of chalk."},{"time":225000,"text":"I picked this up at MIT. It's a little younger."},{"time":228000,"text":"And it's different than this limestone, you can see that."},{"time":230000,"text":"You wouldn't build a building out of this stuff,"},{"time":232000,"text":"and you wouldn't try to give a lecture and write on the chalkboard with this."},{"time":235000,"text":"Yeah, it's very different -- no, it's not different."},{"time":237000,"text":"It's not different, it's the same stuff:"},{"time":239000,"text":"calcium carbonate, calcium carbonate."},{"time":242000,"text":"What's different is how the molecules are put together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"Now, if you think that's kind of neat,"},{"time":248000,"text":"the story gets really neat right now."},{"time":251000,"text":"Off the coast of California comes this:"},{"time":254000,"text":"It's an abalone shell."},{"time":256000,"text":"Now, millions of abalone every year"},{"time":258000,"text":"make this shell."},{"time":260000,"text":"Oh, by the way, just in case you weren't already guessing,"},{"time":262000,"text":"it's calcium carbonate."},{"time":264000,"text":"It's the same stuff as this"},{"time":266000,"text":"and the same stuff as this."},{"time":268000,"text":"But it's not the same stuff; it's different."},{"time":270000,"text":"It's thousands of times,"},{"time":272000,"text":"maybe 3,000 times tougher than this."},{"time":275000,"text":"And why? Because the lowly abalone"},{"time":278000,"text":"is able to lay down"},{"time":280000,"text":"the calcium carbonate crystals in layers,"},{"time":282000,"text":"making this beautiful, iridescent"},{"time":284000,"text":"mother of pearl."},{"time":286000,"text":"Very specialized material"},{"time":288000,"text":"that the abalone self-assembles,"},{"time":290000,"text":"millions of abalone,"},{"time":292000,"text":"all the time, every day, every year."},{"time":294000,"text":"This is pretty incredible stuff."},{"time":296000,"text":"All the same, what's different?"},{"time":298000,"text":"How the molecules are put together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300000,"text":"Now, what does this have to do with energy?"},{"time":303000,"text":"Here's a piece of coal."},{"time":305000,"text":"And I'll suggest that this coal"},{"time":307000,"text":"is about as exciting"},{"time":309000,"text":"as this chalk."},{"time":312000,"text":"Now, whether we're talking about fuels"},{"time":314000,"text":"or energy carriers,"},{"time":316000,"text":"or perhaps novel materials for batteries"},{"time":318000,"text":"or fuel cells,"},{"time":320000,"text":"nature hasn't ever built those perfect materials yet"},{"time":323000,"text":"because nature didn't need to."},{"time":325000,"text":"Nature didn't need to because, unlike the abalone shell,"},{"time":328000,"text":"the survival of a species didn't depend"},{"time":331000,"text":"on building those materials,"},{"time":333000,"text":"until maybe now when it might just matter."},{"time":337000,"text":"So, when we think about the future of energy,"},{"time":340000,"text":"imagine"},{"time":342000,"text":"what would it be like"},{"time":344000,"text":"if instead of this,"},{"time":346000,"text":"we could build the energy equivalent of this"},{"time":350000,"text":"just by rearranging the molecules differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"And so that is my story."},{"time":356000,"text":"The oil will never run out."},{"time":358000,"text":"It's not because we have a lot of it."},{"time":360000,"text":"It's not because we're going to build a bajillion windmills."},{"time":363000,"text":"It's because, well,"},{"time":366000,"text":"thousands of years ago,"},{"time":368000,"text":"people invented ideas --"},{"time":370000,"text":"they had ideas, innovations, technology --"},{"time":372000,"text":"and the Stone Age ended,"},{"time":375000,"text":"not because we ran out of stones."},{"time":377000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":379000,"text":"It's ideas, it's innovation, it's technology"},{"time":382000,"text":"that will end the age of oil, long before we run out of oil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}